2ee6f4e70a91ea95072d9ed09d610ff33ca320c6.query:
SELECT
                signing_keypair
                    AS "signing_keypair: KeyPair",
                revocation_commitment_parameters
                    AS "revocation_commitment_parameters: CommitmentParameters",
                range_proof_parameters
                    AS "range_proof_parameters: RangeProofParameters"
            FROM
                merchant_config

46ea459c9d2e371ace67299de61c55d6e17a6c8b.query:
SELECT secret AS "secret: RevocationSecret"
            FROM revocations
            WHERE lock = ?

866f68c59d036e6c895aaaa65aad6b2805ece96b.query: INSERT INTO nonces (data) VALUES (?) ON CONFLICT (data) DO NOTHING

aa91a624c3efb7bbda7d2501c6b93f13513b36b9.query:
INSERT INTO
                merchant_config
            (signing_keypair, revocation_commitment_parameters, range_proof_parameters)
                VALUES
